org.geppetto.model

Interface GeppettoModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeppettoModelImpl

    public interface GeppettoModel
    A representation of the model object 'Model'. The root of every Geppetto model

    The following features are supported:

    • Variables
    • Libraries
    • Tags
    • Id
    • Name
    • Data Sources
    • Queries
    See Also:
    GeppettoPackage.getGeppettoModel()
